{"tid":616520,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] King’s Raid #104 又係時候曬命","createTime":"2018-04-04T08:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T08:40:20.000Z","uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"62b57cfd68f0d4b6af0df055f0f316a88aaa19dd","tid":616520,"uid":71021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:31:19.000Z","msg":"197d無on鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當年佢抽咗Aisha把專開心咗幾日都無就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/203533_9eb61083b42044350f88a571d1e0dede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F203533_9eb61083b42044350f88a571d1e0dede.jpg&h=bb5ce285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/23/203536_8d2f4cbaa398067b0bf8ea73320ebdfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F23%2F203536_8d2f4cbaa398067b0bf8ea73320ebdfe.jpg&h=d3b44728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/388803/page/33\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/388803/page/33</a><br />\n由#806開始追即可[/member]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>新手巴絲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span></span>亂入公會，要入就入Lihkg公會<br />\n因為你一入錯，要退會入Lihkg公會，就要等足七日先會有奬勵你拎<br />\n唔使問有無位，搵到即係有，搵唔到即係無<br />\n申請咗邊個公會+ID麻煩填表，優先處理填表巴絲<br />\n填完麻煩再係Post度留名話自己填咗表，即有專人為你服務</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只限日服適用 - 刷首抽Q&amp;A</strong></span></span><br />\n所有Q&amp;A僅供參考，各巴絲可自行選擇有愛之英雄作為目標<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點解我無得抽嘅？</span><br />\nA：麻煩出Game再入Game睇下自己揀咗咩Ser，目前只有日服先會有得刷廿抽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：點樣拎廿抽？</span><br />\nA：打完頭三關教學任務，去右上角信箱拎石同十抽卷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Q：抽邊個Pool好？點解？</span><br />\nA：首推刺客Pool<br />\n因為每隻英都會有個人專用嘅<br />\nUW = Unique Weapon <br />\nUT = Unique Treasure<br />\n兩樣係唔同嘅裝備，裝嘅位置唔一樣，可以同時使用，將隻英發揮到最大嘅效果<br />\n因為有52隻英，咁就唔一一貼上嚟<br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UT、UW、Artifact整合英文版：<br />\n<a href=\"https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaskofgoblin.netlify.com%2F%3Fitem%3DKasel&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a714203c\" target=\"_blank\">https://maskofgoblin.netlify.com/?item=Kasel</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄Skill、UW整合殘體中文版：(非最新版本，所以麻煩連埋第一頁全攻略嚟睇)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D12943067%26rand%3D824&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=df27e4a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=12943067&amp;rand=824</a><br />\n<br />\n全英雄UT殘體中文版：(如果唔知佢講啲英係邊隻去上面全人物圖鑑對/直接問)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.ngacn.cc%2Fread.php%3Ftid%3D13705992&d=nUikO4GnJTZNsawTfVuaS26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=7384ffc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.ngacn.cc/read.php?tid=13705992</a>"},{"pid":"8a29f9ff6cefd20b6756384ab060cf15c86141e1","tid":616520,"uid":134365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"話又中左姐...<br />\n點會唔想要..<br />\n好彩5星卷忍痛簡左maria..<br />\n而家有得升星, 開心都黎唔切...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e345592bc1fc89b87af349639d09e159d7ad69f","tid":616520,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"個第一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1958f9f1f2792a563ec0f96049531bed91e6da5d","tid":616520,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,